import { Tabs,Tab, Toolbar, Typography,  } from '@mui/material';
import AppBar from '@mui/material/AppBar';
 
export const Navbar=()=>{
 
 

    return( 
        <>
        <AppBar elevation={0}>
            <Toolbar disableGutters  sx={{ p: 3,ml:5 }} >
               <Tabs sx={{ display: 'flex'   }}>
                   <Tab >
                   <Typography>
                       Logo
                   </Typography>
                   </Tab>
                   <Tab  label='HOME'/>
                   <Tab label='What is GPT?'/>
                   <Tab label='OPEN AI'/>
                   <Tab label='CASE STUDIES'/>
                   <Tab label='Library'/>

               </Tabs>
            </Toolbar>
          
        </AppBar>
        </>
    )
}
